p: According to results, Cfa and Bwk climate provided relatively positive correlation with PH, FL, BN, FW, DW, SW, Ca, Car, and antioxidant enzymes and negative correlation with LL, LW, LA, LN, SD, SLA, Cb, TC, and TP. In Csa and Bsa climate, the results were the opposite of the above. The traits were not very affected by the Dsa climate ( Table 6A).
